high_descs: Turn around and walk to the long couch between the two chairs.
Pick up the keys that are closest to the edge, in the center of the couch.
Turn around and walk toward the fireplace, stopping at the coffee table.
Place the keys on the corner of the table, closest to the fireplace.
Walk between the fireplace and the table to get to the shelf under the TV.
Pick up the keys close to the edge of the shelf.
Turn to your right and go back to the end of the table.
Place the keys on the table, between the other set of keys and the watch.
anns.task_desc: Put two sets of keys on the coffee table.

high_descs: Turn around, go forward, turn around the coffee table, go to the middle of the couch, turn left
Pick up the keys closer to the edge of the couch
Turn left, go forward, turn right at the edge of the coffee table, go a bit forward, turn left
Put the keys on the coffee table
Turn right, go forward a bit, turn right, go in front of the television, turn right
Pick up the keys near the television
Turn left, go to the edge of the coffee table, turn right, go forward a bit, turn right
Put the keys on the coffee table
anns.task_desc: Bring two set of keys to the coffee table

high_descs: Turn around, go forward, turn left before reaching the coffee table, go forward to the couch, turn right, go to the middle couch cushion, face the couch.
Take the closest keys from the couch cushion.
Turn left, go forward a step, turn left, go forward, turn left to face the coffee table.
Put the keys on the corner of the coffee table closest to the fire place.
Turn right, go forward, turn left, go in front of the TV and face the TV.
Take the keys in front of the TV.
Turn right, go back to the side of the coffee table.
Put the keys to the left of the first keys.
anns.task_desc: Put two keys on a coffee table.
